trans-unit.source: Contains the data sent to the tracking service by the runtime tracking infrastructure when it matches a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder data som er sendt til Sporingstjenesten av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur når den samsvarer med en <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: It is also used in the return list of the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.WorkflowEvents*> property.
trans-unit.target: Den brukes også i return listen over den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.WorkflowEvents*>egenskapen.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.WorkflowEvents*>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] When the runtime tracking infrastructure matches a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint> in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>, it sends a WorkflowTrackingRecord to the tracking service over the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> associated with that tracking service.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Når runtime sporing infrastruktur samsvarer med en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>i en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>, sendes en WorkflowTrackingRecord til Sporingstjenesten den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>som er forbundet med denne Sporingstjenesten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: The tracking service can perform whatever action is necessary on the data in the tracking record.
trans-unit.target: Sporingstjenesten kan utføre hvilken handling er nødvendig på dataene i sporing-oppføringen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets an <xref:System.EventArgs> that contains additional data associated with certain types of workflow status events.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en <xref:System.EventArgs>som inneholder flere data som er knyttet til bestemte hendelsestypene arbeidsflyten status.</xref:System.EventArgs>

trans-unit.source: For most workflow status events, EventArgs is a null reference (`Nothing`); however, for certain kinds of workflow status events the runtime tracking infrastructure uses EventArgs to return additional data about the workflow status event.
trans-unit.target: EventArgs kan er et nullreferanse for de fleste arbeidsflyten Statushendelser (`Nothing`); imidlertid for bestemte typer arbeidsflyten Statushendelser bruker runtime sporing infrastruktur EventArgs kan til å returnere ytterligere data om arbeidsflyten status for hendelsen.

trans-unit.target: Følgende tabell lister av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent>verdier som svarer til disse spesielle arbeidsflyten statusen hendelsene og objekttypen returnert i EventArgs kan for hvert enkelt av disse arbeidsflyten statusen hendelsene.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent>

trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.DateTime>som angir datoen og klokkeslettet arbeidsflyten status for hendelsen inntraff.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates the order in the workflow instance of the workflow status event that matched the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir rekkefølgen arbeidsflytforekomsten av arbeidsflyten status for hendelsen som samsvarer med den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: EventOrder indicates the relative order in the workflow instance of the workflow status event that matched the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder angir relativ rekkefølgen arbeidsflytforekomsten av arbeidsflyten status for hendelsen som samsvarer med <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: EventOrder is unique within a workflow instance, but it is not guaranteed to be sequential.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder er unikt innenfor en arbeidsflytforekomst, men garanteres ikke være sammenhengende.

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er angitt av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: A value that indicates the order of the workflow status event in the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: En verdi som angir rekkefølgen av arbeidsflyten status for hendelsen i arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the type of workflow status event associated with the tracking record.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir hendelsestypen arbeidsflyten statusen tilknyttet sporingsposten.

trans-unit.source: `TrackingWorkflowEvent` contains one of the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent> values indicating the kind of workflow status event that was matched by the runtime tracking infrastructure and caused the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord> to be sent.
trans-unit.target: `TrackingWorkflowEvent`inneholder én av de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent>verdier som angir hvilken type arbeidsflyten status for hendelsen som samsvarer med kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur og forårsaket av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord>sendes.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent>

trans-unit.source: It reflects the current status of the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Den gjenspeiler gjeldende status for arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.source: A workflow instance emits workflow status events only when the status of the workflow instance changes, and, therefore, a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint> can be matched only when a workflow status change occurs.
trans-unit.target: En arbeidsflytforekomst avgir arbeidsflyten Statushendelser bare når statusen til arbeidsflytforekomsten endres, og derfor en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>samsvarer bare når en arbeidsflyt statusendring skjer.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er angitt av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent"> </xref> verdier.
